== Black Goose

== README


We are using Devise 3.0 (I believe) for account authentication.

We currently have semi-functional escort and client accounts (i.e. you can make
and sign in with accounts)!

12/9 - Created Appointment Table

* Looking for a good method for creating an appointment given a time slot.
Need to look into calendar gems for this.

12/20

* Spent a lot of time trying to work with Microsoft Azure

* You can now make unrestricted appointments (i.e. no validations)


